16:14.550 --> 16:15.080
我在

16:18.750 --> 16:19.550
How are you

16:23.390 --> 16:23.720
Fine

16:23.720 --> 16:24.380
Thank you

16:25.120 --> 16:25.670
And you

16:39.440 --> 16:41.670
一百九十七天了

16:42.870 --> 16:43.840
